# Ship Testing Convention

During ship review, run **incremental tests** instead of the full suite:

- Use the project's incremental test command which only runs tests related to uncommitted changes
- Only fall back to full test suite when explicitly requested or when changes touch shared infrastructure (e.g. test config, tsconfig, dependency files)
